SYNOPSIS

     use Log::ger::Output Callback => (
         logging_cb   => sub { my ($ctx, $numlevel, $msg) = @_; ... }, # optional
         detection_cb => sub { my ($numlevel) = @_; ... },             # optional
     );

DESCRIPTION

CONFIGURATION

logging_cb => code

detection_cb => code

SEE ALSO

    Log::ger

    Modelled after Log::Any::Adapter::Callback

